Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This entity represents a product that a customer would buy which contains the product details as attributes. It has a many-many relationship with Order and many-one relationship with designer and many to one with customer
